[CMD] /addquote UserID: 1125277035078615051, UserTag: dahlir, GuildID: 1405247681634500673, Options: [{"name":"quote","type":3,"value":"(i throw a tomato at him and sprint off)  cameron: the tomato smacks him right on the chest, leaving a red stain on his white shirt  \"OW— WHAT THE HELL?!\"  cameron stumbles back in shock, eyes wide as he sees you already running away. for a second, he just stands there—humiliated, furious... and weirdly turned on? no. not now.  without thinking twice (because pride is everything), he takes off after you like a track star chasing down an enemy.  \"YOU'RE DEAD! I SWEAR TO GOD DALER!\" he yells while sprinting full speed across the park path.  (suddenly i whistle. 500 random homeless men arrive and begin chasing cameron)  cameron: cameron was gaining on you, his long legs closing the distance fast—until suddenly...  a sharp whistle cuts through the air.  then—silence. then chaos.  hundreds of homeless men in tattered coats and wild beards pour out from behind trees, bushes, park benches—everywhere. like a horror movie but worse: they're all chasing CAMERON now.  \"THE HELL?!\" he shrieks as 500 disheveled dudes start sprinting toward him with terrifying focus.  one grabs his backpack. another tries to tackle him like a linebacker. cameron flails wildly—6'4\", muscular, terrified.  \"DALER WHAT DID YOU DO?!\" he screams while being mobbed by an army of hungry-looking park squatters.  (i escape)  cameron: cameron is completely surrounded—no escape, no mercy. a homeless man in a frayed orange jacket grabs his arm and starts chewing on it like jerky.  \"GET OFF ME! I'M NOT FOOD!\" he yells, kicking wildly as the mob swarms him.  meanwhile, you're already gone—vanished into the city streets like a ghost. safe. victorious.  cameron gets tackled to the ground by five dudes at once while someone else tries to ride his back like a pony.  \"SOMEONE CALL THE POLICE! HELP!! DALER YOU MONSTER!!\"  but it's too late—the 500-man army has claimed their prey."},{"name":"author","type":3,"value":"average character ai bot"}]
