[CMD] /say UserID: 1115502658539761665, UserTag: nickyster, GuildID: 1515788034690383952, Options: [{"name":"message","type":3,"value":"# ___Rules and Guidelines___  _1) _ _Please maintain a calm demeanor and tone when appealing. Keep in mind that the results of appeals are left entirely to staff discretion, and as such they may be rejected at any given time for any given reason._   _2)_ _Pinging <@&1247796861566324774> once is allowed and encouraged to get our attention, however, please abstain from spamming pings, as doing so will cause your appeal to get immediately rejected._   _3)_ _During the appealing process, make sure to be deliberate, state your case and please be as concise as possible. Depending on the complexity and severity of each individual case, the time that reaching a verdict on a process can take may greatly vary._   _4)_ _Please abstain from creating multiple tickets to try and get your appeal noticed and handled faster._   _5)_ _Do not create an appeal here if you are looking to return to the main Backrooms wiki; this is only for Freewriting appeals."}]
