[CMD] /embed UserID: 1115502658539761665, UserTag: nickyster, GuildID: 1500900336674541659, Options: [{"name":"title","type":3,"value":"Server Rules"},{"name":"description","type":3,"value":"# *__Server Rules__* <br>  ## 1) Discord TOS <br> *This should be obvious. Follow Discord's TOS.* <br> ## 2) No NSFW/NSFL <br> *Inappropriate, harmful content and discussions are strictly prohibited. A good rule of thumb: If an average person would feel disturbed seeing it in public, do not post it.* <br> ### 2.1) Exceptions <br> *Explicit language and discussion over fictional gore/violence is tolerated. If you believe it goes too far, however, please ping a staff member.* <br> ## 3) Be Mature <br> *We expect all members to handle themselves with decorum while on the server. Serious discussions should be met with earnestness and respect.* <br> ### 3.1) Roleplay <br> *Roleplay is only allowed in <#1505424926067134618> and in forums. Anything else is a no.* <br> ## 4) Channel Use <br> *Please keep conversations in their correct channel. It is difficult to sort through unorganized chats.* <br> ## 5) No Bigotry <br> *Bigotry is not allowed. We have a zero-tolerance policy for hate toward people based on their identity, background, beliefs, or personal characteristics.* <br> ### 5.1) No Slurs <br> *Usage of slurs in any form would be met with punishment, regardless of intent.* <br> ### 5.2) Automod <br> *Certain topics, such as politically sensitive subjects like the Middle East, should be handled with care. Do not use common interest as an excuse to make an excessive amount of jokes on the topic. <br> ## 6) Arguments <br> *Arguments are bound to happen. If you are in one, you can either be respectful or leave it.* <br> ### 6.1) Excessive Arguments <br> *If the argument becomes a matter of personal attacks, rather than anything informed, you are free to ping staff and explain the issue to them.* <br> ## 7) Final Say <br> *Staff and Janitors have the final say in a matter. Their opinion should be respected.* <br> ### 7.1) Corrections <br> *If you disagree with a moderation decision, contact another staff member. Do not try doing it yourself."},{"name":"channel","type":7,"value":"1500901764038136011","channel":{"type":0,"guild":"1500900336674541659","guildId":"1500900336674541659","permissionOverwrites":["1500900336674541659","1500903701458452531","1505370191616278570","1501273466811318334","1500904098860498974"],"messages":["1515850557389017179","1515850556525248552"],"threads":[],"nsfw":false,"flags":0,"id":"1500901764038136011","name":"🔒｜private-staff-chat","rawPosition":29,"parentId":"1500987003309916160","topic":null,"lastMessageId":"1515850557389017179","lastPinTimestamp":1780792064356,"defaultThreadRateLimitPerUser":null,"rateLimitPerUser":0,"createdTimestamp":1777913265953}}]
